RotaToy is a lightweight full-stack application designed to manage recurring item/task rotation workflows.

Current features include:
- Task/item rotation management
- Basic action tracking
- Responsive UI
- REST API integration
- CRUD operations for recurring workflows

## Current Limitations

- No authentication yet
- Single-user focused workflow
- No notifications/reminders
- Limited analytics/reporting

## Future Improvements

- User authentication and roles
- Calendar integration
- Push/email reminders
- Drag-and-drop scheduling
- Dashboard and analytics
- Mobile optimization
- Docker deployment
